  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Forus Bank Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC proposes to provide a loan facility for IFCs own account of up to 5.0 million to FORUS Bank (the bank), of which 3.0 million would be the A Tranche amd 2.0 million will be in the form of a stand-by tranche that would become available after the bank is fully capitalized.  The loan will be used to support the banks microfinance lending operations during its formative years of operations.  The loan is expected to be Ruble-linked, to avoid any currency mismatch on the banks balance sheet.</narrative>
  </description>
